Thought	#451.	 deep musing &c. (intent). in the mind, under consideration. Adv. all things considered. Phr. the mind being on the stretch
Inattention	#458.	 preoccupation, distraction, reverie, brown study, deep musing, fit of abstraction. V. be inattentive &c. adj.
Inattention	#458.	 dreaming on other things, musing on other things
Dejection	#837.	 thick-ey'd musing and curs'd melancholy" [Henry IV]
